BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Paint & Sip
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T180000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260424T200000
UID:92fdee9be8cfdbe627f6c7e7b23078ba@cityofevanston.org
DESCRIPTION:Unleash your inner artist at Prieto's first paint and sip even
 t! Join us for a relaxing and creative evening full of laughter and good c
 ompany. Whether you're an experienced artist\, looking for a way to relax\
 , or even looking for a fun date night\, this is the event for you! Regist
 ration is per person and will include one alcoholic beverage and light sna
 cks. Additional alcohol will be available for purchase.
LOCATION:Prieto Community Center\, 430 Asbury Ave.
URL:https://app.amilia.com/store/en/cityofevanston/shop/activities/6688962
X-SOURCE:City of Evanston
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Earth Day Fest
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260425T100000
DTEND;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260425T140000
UID:3b3775606af7e6b3797e53d5d28dec14@cityofevanston.org
DESCRIPTION:Join the Ecology Center in celebrating and giving back to the 
 environment during Earth Day Festivities. Enjoy a week of free programs le
 ading up to Earth Day\, presented in collaboration with local environmenta
 l organizations. The celebration wraps up on Saturday with Earth Day Fest\
 , featuring hands-on activities like litter clean-up and planting projects
  in the Ladd Arboretum.
LOCATION:Evanston Ecology Center\, 2024 N McCormick Blvd.
X-SOURCE:City of Evanston
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
